            The Aspose.Cells.GridWeb is shipped with a built-in Aspose.Cells.GridWeb Designer. You may activate
            the designer in two ways, from System Start menu or from the Visual Studio IDE.
            In Visual Studio, right click the Grid Control in a webform, then select &quot;Aspose.Cells.GridWeb
            Designer...&quot; from the popup menu.</p>
        <p>
            With the designer, you can:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Set the control's display styles. Load/Save style XML files. Create your style files.</li>
